    "plan_content": "Here's the complete plan for implementing the `Stepper` component:\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### 4 file operations — no existing component files touched\n\n#### Create 2 new files:\n\n**1. `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/stepper.tsx`**\n\nA `\"use client\"` compound component with **two React contexts**:\n- `StepperContext` (root) → shares `value`, `onValueChange`, `orientation`\n- `StepperItemContext` (per item) → shares `step`, `isActive`, `isCompleted`\n\n**9 exported sub-components + 1 hook:**\n\n| Export | Element | Role |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Stepper` | `<div>` | Root context provider; `group/stepper` for CSS group selectors; controlled + uncontrolled |\n| `StepperList` | `<nav>` | `flex-row` (horizontal) / `flex-col` (vertical) via group selectors |\n| `StepperItem` | `<div>` | Item context provider; `data-state=\"active\\|completed\\|inactive\"` |\n| `StepperTrigger` | `<button>` | Calls `onValueChange(step)`; `aria-current=\"step\"` when active |\n| `StepperIndicator` | `<span>` | Step number or `<CheckIcon>` when completed; `data-[state=...]` ring styling |\n| `StepperTitle` | `<p>` | `text-sm font-medium` |\n| `StepperDescription` | `<p>` | `text-xs text-muted-foreground` |\n| `StepperSeparator` | `<div>` | `h-px flex-1` (horizontal) / `h-8 w-px ml-4` (vertical) — via group selectors |\n| `StepperPanel` | `<div>` | Returns `null` when step ≠ active |\n| `useStepper()` | hook | Throws if called outside `<Stepper>` |\n\nOrientation handled exclusively via Tailwind group selectors (`group-data-[orientation=horizontal]/stepper:...`) — same pattern as `tabs.tsx`. No Radix UI dependency needed.\n\n**2. `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/examples/stepper-demo.tsx`**\n\nInteractive 3-step horizontal wizard (Account → Profile → Review) with `Button` Previous/Next navigation, `StepperPanel` content areas, and `StepperSeparator` between items.\n\n---\n\n#### Modify 2 existing files (append registry entries only):\n\n**3. `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/_registry.ts`** — Insert between `\"spinner\"` and `\"switch\"` (~line 563):\n```ts\n{ name: \"stepper\", type: \"registry:ui\", files: [{ path: \"ui/stepper.tsx\", type: \"registry:ui\" }] }\n```\nNo `dependencies` field (lucide-react is implicit like `accordion`; no Radix UI).\n\n**4. `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/examples/_registry.ts`** — Insert between `\"spinner-item\"` and `\"switch-demo\"` (~line 2124):\n```ts\n{ name: \"stepper-demo\", type: \"registry:example\", registryDependencies: [\"stepper\", \"button\"], files: [...] }\n```\n\n---\n\n**Verification:** TypeScript check (`tsc --noEmit`), lint, and visual inspection via dev server. Confirm `git diff --name-only` shows exactly 4 files.",
